0.1.name: wordpress/oronjowordpressplugin
0.1.description: The Oronjo Wordpress Plug allows you to easily import/update your Oronjo content into your Wordpress blog. This makes selling your intangibles a very easy process! With Oronjo you can sell articles on your weblog; chapters of your novel; your best MP3 mixes; your thesis; Hi-res versions of your photos; or your homemade movies. There is no need for a secure section on your site and you don't need a PayPal or Checkout account. Our service is 100% free. Oronjo interfaces with Paypal and Google Checkout. You can now also sell your content in Euros. There will be an Oronjo OpenSocial gadget soon!
